ĮTo honour
Thomas J. Johnston of San Francisco
Who visited these gardens as a Commander in the
US Navy during the Normandy Landings and
later with his family and President of his company"Ū
─In loving memory of Sir Francis (Bob) and Lady (Pat) Purchas
who were part of the Inn for many years and loved the gardens,
given by their sons Christopher and Robin on behalf of all the family."═
╩[Bench Back]
In memory of "King" Richard Niazi, whose passion for life
and generosity of spirit was an inspiration to all.

[UNDER SEAT]
A lover of and forever loved by Covent Garden. December 2008"ų
